{"id":148544,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：奥巴马承诺助受灾民众重建/","date":"2011-04-29T08:30:23Z","modified":"2011-04-29T08:30:23Z","title":"简讯：奥巴马承诺助受灾民众重建","content":"<div>\n<p>美国总统奥巴马承诺政府将尽全力帮助美国南部遭受龙卷风灾害的民众重建家园。</p>\n<p>美国南部数州一个星期来已经接连遭到近300个龙卷风的袭击。</p>\n<p>其中星期三（4月27日）灾情最为严重，一天内出现了150多个龙卷风。</p>\n<p>风灾已经造成至少281人死亡。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/AM52LtDHp5N055ISRTU5ciQSVvU/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/AM52LtDHp5N055ISRTU5ciQSVvU/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/AM52LtDHp5N055ISRTU5ciQSVvU/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/AM52LtDHp5N055ISRTU5ciQSVvU/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/29f8eLoq1cY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}